纽约—特朗普担任总统九个月后，共和党领导人似乎终于清醒地认识到严峻的现实：这个国家正站在深渊边缘。 ==>  the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the
