这一点随着斯大林的掌权而发生了改变。对斯大林来说，恐怖既是手段，也是目的。 ==>  the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the
