今天，任何认为不那么早与特朗普决裂也不会对自身名誉造成不可逆转的损失的共和党人，都应该回忆一下其他人的命运——1917年的苏联人、1932年的德国人，以及今天的俄罗斯人和土耳其人——这些人都认为他们能够驯服魔鬼。 ==> And any Republicans today who think they can delay breaking definitively with Trump, without irreversibly damaging their own reputations, should recall the fate of others – in the Soviet Union in 1917, in Germany in 1932, and in Russia and Turkey today – who thought they could tame a monster. 
