托洛茨基出局后，斯大林将矛头转向了所有其他布尔什维克高层，说他们是“人民的敌人”——特朗普的民粹主义支持者们，比如英国的强硬退欧派，让这个词死灰复燃，拿它来谴责所有胆敢挑战他们的“血和土”（bloodandsoil）信条的人。 ==> Once Trotsky was out of the way, Stalin turned on all the other senior Bolsheviks, calling them “enemies of the people” – a phrase that Trump’s populist supporters, like United Kingdom’s hardline Brexiteers, have revived to denounce anyone who dares challenge their “blood and soil” code. 
