作为一名理性的、有技术官僚倾向的政客，巴本认为，他能够在希特勒掌权后控制住这位自吹自擂的外省人纳粹领袖。 ==>  the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the
