布尔什维克革命十多年后，布哈林试图让自己对“无产阶级专政”的学术理解与其真实世界的含义协调起来。 ==> For more than a decade after the Bolshevik Revolution, Bukharin tried to reconcile his academic understanding of “the dictatorship of proletariat” with its real-world implementation. 
布尔什维克革命十多年后，布哈林试图让自己对“无产阶级专政”的学术理解与其真实世界的含义协调起来。 ==>  the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the
