尽管如此，布哈林仍然配合斯大林清洗托洛茨基和其他坚守列宁遗训（以及他对斯大林的不利批评）的布尔什维克。 ==> Nonetheless, Bukharin aligned with Stalin to purge Leon Trotsky and other Bolsheviks who sought to adhere more closely to Lenin’s dictates (and his testament against Stalin). 
尽管如此，布哈林仍然配合斯大林清洗托洛茨基和其他坚守列宁遗训（以及他对斯大林的不利批评）的布尔什维克。 ==>  the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the the
